    "These values were obtained through confirmatory factor analysis, which serves as a robust method for testing both validity and reliability.",
    "Assessments of model fitness for employee engagement constructThe RMSEA value for this particular model is 0.066, which falls within the range of close fit, as a value below 0.08 is considered to indicate a good fit according to Cudeck et al. [9] and Steiger [51].",
    "Additionally, the preci- sion of the RMSEA estimate can be assessed through the point estimate, which represents the lower boundary of the confidence interval.",
    "In this case, the lower bound of the model is 0.046, which is below the suggested close fit value of 0.05 according to MacCallum et al. [41].",
    "Consequently, the model is considered to be a close fit for the given data."
